{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"One morning, in the year 1957,"},{"time":4000,"text":"the neurosurgeon Wilder Penfield"},{"time":7000,"text":"saw himself like this,"},{"time":10000,"text":"a weird freak with huge hands,"},{"time":13000,"text":"huge mouth,"},{"time":15000,"text":"and a tiny bottom."},{"time":18000,"text":"Actually this creature"},{"time":21000,"text":"is the result of the Penfield research."},{"time":23000,"text":"He named it homunculus."},{"time":25000,"text":"Basically the homunculus is"},{"time":28000,"text":"the visualization of a human being"},{"time":30000,"text":"where each part of the body is proportional"},{"time":33000,"text":"to the surface it takes in the brain."},{"time":36000,"text":"So, of course, homunculus is definitely not a freak."},{"time":41000,"text":"It's you. It's me."},{"time":43000,"text":"It's our invisible reality."},{"time":46000,"text":"This visualization could explain, for example,"},{"time":49000,"text":"why newborns, or smokers,"},{"time":52000,"text":"put, instinctively, their fingers in the mouth."},{"time":55000,"text":"Unfortunately it doesn't explain why"},{"time":59000,"text":"so many designers remain mainly interested"},{"time":62000,"text":"in designing chairs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64000,"text":"So anyway, even if I do not understand science entirely,"},{"time":67000,"text":"for my design I essentially refer to it."},{"time":70000,"text":"I'm fascinated by its ability to"},{"time":73000,"text":"deeply investigate the human being,"},{"time":75000,"text":"its way of working, its way of feeling."},{"time":78000,"text":"And it really helps me to understand"},{"time":81000,"text":"how we see, how we hear,"},{"time":83000,"text":"how we breathe, how our brain can inform or mislead us."},{"time":88000,"text":"It's a great tool for me"},{"time":90000,"text":"to understand what could be our real needs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94000,"text":"Marketing people have never been able to do that."},{"time":98000,"text":"Marketing reduces things. Marketing simplifies."},{"time":101000,"text":"Marketing creates user groups."},{"time":104000,"text":"And scientists, amidst complexity,"},{"time":107000,"text":"amidst fluctuation and uniqueness."},{"time":110000,"text":"What could be our real needs?"},{"time":112000,"text":"Maybe the silence."},{"time":114000,"text":"In our daily life we are continuously disturbed by"},{"time":116000,"text":"aggressive sounds."},{"time":118000,"text":"And you know all those kind of sound puts us"},{"time":120000,"text":"in a kind of stressful state,"},{"time":122000,"text":"and prevent us from being quiet and focused."},{"time":125000,"text":"So I wanted to create a kind of"},{"time":127000,"text":"sound filter,"},{"time":130000,"text":"able to preserve ourselves from noise pollution."},{"time":132000,"text":"But I didn't want it to make it by"},{"time":135000,"text":"isolating people, without any earmuffs"},{"time":138000,"text":"or those kind of things."},{"time":140000,"text":"Or neither with including complex technology."},{"time":143000,"text":"I just wanted to, using the complexity"},{"time":147000,"text":"and the technology of the brain, of the human brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150000,"text":"So I worked with white noise."},{"time":153000,"text":"dB is basically --"},{"time":155000,"text":"dB is the name of the product,"},{"time":157000,"text":"basically a white noise diffuser."},{"time":159000,"text":"This is white noise."},{"time":160000,"text":"The white noise is the sum of all frequencies"},{"time":163000,"text":"that are audible by the human being,"},{"time":165000,"text":"brought to the same intensity."},{"time":167000,"text":"And this noise is like a \"shhhhhhhhhhhhh,\" like that."},{"time":172000,"text":"And this noise is the most neutral."},{"time":174000,"text":"It is the perfect sound for our ears and our brain."},{"time":177000,"text":"So when you hear this sound"},{"time":179000,"text":"you feel like a kind of shelter,"},{"time":182000,"text":"preserved from noise pollution."},{"time":185000,"text":"And when you hear the white noise, your brain is immediately focused on it."},{"time":188000,"text":"And do not be disturbed any more by the other aggressive sound."},{"time":192000,"text":"It seems to be magic."},{"time":194000,"text":"But it is just physiology. It's just in your brain."},{"time":197000,"text":"And in mine, I hope."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200000,"text":"So in order to make this white noise"},{"time":203000,"text":"a little bit active and reactive,"},{"time":205000,"text":"I create a ball, a rolling ball"},{"time":208000,"text":"able to analyze and find"},{"time":212000,"text":"where does aggressive sound come from,"},{"time":214000,"text":"and roll, at home or at work,"},{"time":217000,"text":"towards aggressive noise,"},{"time":220000,"text":"and emits white noise in order to neutralize it."},{"time":223000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":226000,"text":"It works."},{"time":240000,"text":"You feel the effect of the white noise?"},{"time":244000,"text":"It's too in silence."},{"time":246000,"text":"If you make some noise you can feel the effect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249000,"text":"So even if this object,"},{"time":252000,"text":"even if this product includes some technology,"},{"time":254000,"text":"it includes some speakers, it includes some microphones"},{"time":256000,"text":"and some electronic devices,"},{"time":259000,"text":"this object is not a very smart object."},{"time":262000,"text":"And I don't want to make a very smart object."},{"time":264000,"text":"I don't want to create a perfect object like a perfect robot."},{"time":268000,"text":"I want to create an object like you and me."},{"time":271000,"text":"So, definitely not perfect."},{"time":273000,"text":"So imagine, for instance, you are at home."},{"time":276000,"text":"A loving dispute with your girl or boyfriend."},{"time":279000,"text":"You shout. You say, \"Blah blah blah, Blah blah blah. Who is this guy?\""},{"time":282000,"text":"And dB will probably roll toward you."},{"time":286000,"text":"And turning around you is \"shhhhhhh,\" like that."},{"time":291000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":292000,"text":"Definitely not perfect. So you would probably"},{"time":294000,"text":"shut it, at this point."},{"time":296000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":298000,"text":"Anyway, in this same kind of approach,"},{"time":301000,"text":"I designed K."},{"time":303000,"text":"K is a daylight receiver transmitter."},{"time":306000,"text":"So this object is supposed to be displayed on your desk,"},{"time":309000,"text":"or on your piano, where you are supposed"},{"time":311000,"text":"to spend most of your time in the day."},{"time":313000,"text":"And this object will be"},{"time":315000,"text":"able to know exactly the quantity of light you receive during the day,"},{"time":318000,"text":"and able to give you the quantity of light you need."},{"time":322000,"text":"This object is completely covered by"},{"time":325000,"text":"fiber opticals."},{"time":327000,"text":"And the idea of those fiber opticals is to inform the object, for sure,"},{"time":330000,"text":"but creates the idea of an"},{"time":333000,"text":"eye sensibility of the object."},{"time":336000,"text":"I want, by this design"},{"time":338000,"text":"feel, when you see it,"},{"time":340000,"text":"you see, instinctively,"},{"time":342000,"text":"this object seems to be very sensitive,"},{"time":344000,"text":"very reactive."},{"time":346000,"text":"And this object knows, better than you"},{"time":349000,"text":"and probably before you, what you really need."},{"time":351000,"text":"You have to know that the lack of daylight"},{"time":353000,"text":"can provoke some"},{"time":356000,"text":"problem of energy, or problem of libido."},{"time":358000,"text":"So, a huge problem."},{"time":361000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":362000,"text":"Most of the projects I work on --"},{"time":364000,"text":"I live in collaboration with scientists."},{"time":366000,"text":"I'm just a designer. So I need them."},{"time":368000,"text":"So there can be some biologists,"},{"time":370000,"text":"psychiatrists, mathematicians, and so on."},{"time":373000,"text":"And I submit them, my intuitions,"},{"time":376000,"text":"my hypothesis, my first ideas."},{"time":378000,"text":"And they react. They told me what is possible, what is impossible."},{"time":381000,"text":"And together we improve the original concept."},{"time":385000,"text":"And we build the project to the end."},{"time":387000,"text":"And this kind of relationship between designer and scientist"},{"time":390000,"text":"started when I was at school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":392000,"text":"Indeed in my studies I was a guinea pig"},{"time":395000,"text":"for a pharmaceutical industry."},{"time":397000,"text":"And the irony for me was"},{"time":400000,"text":"of course, I didn't do that for the sake of science progress."},{"time":403000,"text":"I just do that to make money."},{"time":405000,"text":"Anyway, this project, or this experience,"},{"time":409000,"text":"make me start a new project on the design of medicine."},{"time":413000,"text":"You have to know that today, roughly one or two every drug pills"},{"time":417000,"text":"is not taken correctly."},{"time":419000,"text":"So even if the active constituents"},{"time":423000,"text":"in pharmaceuticals made constant progress"},{"time":425000,"text":"in terms of chemistry, target of stability,"},{"time":428000,"text":"the behavior of the patients"},{"time":430000,"text":"goes more and more unstable."},{"time":433000,"text":"So we took too many of them."},{"time":436000,"text":"We took irregular dosage."},{"time":439000,"text":"We do not follow instructions. And so on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442000,"text":"So I wanted to create a"},{"time":444000,"text":"new kind of medicine,"},{"time":446000,"text":"in order to create a new kind of relationship"},{"time":448000,"text":"between the patient and the treatment."},{"time":451000,"text":"So I turned traditional pills into this."},{"time":454000,"text":"I'm going to give you some example."},{"time":456000,"text":"This one is an antibiotic."},{"time":459000,"text":"And its purpose is to help patient"},{"time":461000,"text":"to go to the end of the treatment."},{"time":464000,"text":"And the concept is to"},{"time":467000,"text":"create a kind of onion,"},{"time":469000,"text":"a kind of structure in layers."},{"time":472000,"text":"So, you start with the darkest one."},{"time":474000,"text":"And you are helped to visualize the duration of the treatment."},{"time":479000,"text":"And you are helped to visualize the decrease of the infection."},{"time":482000,"text":"So the first day, this is the big one."},{"time":486000,"text":"And you have to peel and eat one layer a day."},{"time":490000,"text":"And your antibiotic goes smaller and clearer."},{"time":493000,"text":"And you're waiting for recovery as you were waiting for the Christmas day."},{"time":497000,"text":"And you follow the treatment like that,"},{"time":501000,"text":"to the end of the treatment."},{"time":503000,"text":"And here you can get the white core."},{"time":505000,"text":"And it means, right, you are in the recovery."},{"time":510000,"text":"(Applause) Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":513000,"text":"This one is a \"third lung,\""},{"time":515000,"text":"a pharmaceutical device for long-term asthma treatment."},{"time":519000,"text":"I designed it to help kids to follow the treatment."},{"time":523000,"text":"So the idea of this one is to create"},{"time":525000,"text":"a relationship between the patient of the treatment"},{"time":528000,"text":"but a relationship of dependency."},{"time":530000,"text":"But in this case it is not the medication that is dependent on the patient."},{"time":534000,"text":"This is, the kids will feel"},{"time":538000,"text":"the therapeutic object needs him."},{"time":541000,"text":"So the idea is, all night long"},{"time":544000,"text":"the elastic skin of the third lung"},{"time":546000,"text":"will slowly inflate itself,"},{"time":548000,"text":"including air and molecules, for sure."},{"time":551000,"text":"And when the kids wake up,"},{"time":553000,"text":"he can see the object needs him. And he take him to his mouth,"},{"time":556000,"text":"and breathe the air it contains."},{"time":558000,"text":"So by this way,"},{"time":560000,"text":"the kid, to take care of himself,"},{"time":564000,"text":"is to take care of this living object."},{"time":567000,"text":"And he does not feel anymore it's relies on asthma treatment,"},{"time":570000,"text":"as the asthma treatment needs him."},{"time":573000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":577000,"text":"In this guise of living object approach,"},{"time":581000,"text":"I like the idea of a kind of invisible design,"},{"time":583000,"text":"as if the function of the object"},{"time":587000,"text":"exists in a kind of invisible field"},{"time":590000,"text":"just around the objects themselves."},{"time":592000,"text":"We could talk about a kind of soul,"},{"time":595000,"text":"of a ghost accompanying them."},{"time":598000,"text":"And almost a kind of poltergeist effect."},{"time":602000,"text":"So when a passive object like this one seems to be alive,"},{"time":605000,"text":"because it is -- woosh -- starting to move."}]},{"cues":[{"time":608000,"text":"And I remember an exhibition design"},{"time":610000,"text":"I made for John Maeda,"},{"time":613000,"text":"and for the Fondation Cartier in Paris."},{"time":615000,"text":"And John Maeda was supposed to show"},{"time":618000,"text":"several graphic animations in this exhibition."},{"time":620000,"text":"And my idea for this exhibition design was to create"},{"time":623000,"text":"a real pong game, like this one."},{"time":626000,"text":"And the idea was to create some self-moving benches"},{"time":629000,"text":"in the main exhibition room."},{"time":631000,"text":"So the living benches would be exactly like the ball."},{"time":634000,"text":"And John was so excited by this idea. He said to me, \"Okay let's go.\""},{"time":639000,"text":"I remember the day of the opening."},{"time":641000,"text":"I was a little bit late."},{"time":643000,"text":"When I bring the 10 living and self-moving benches"},{"time":648000,"text":"in the exhibition room, John was just beside me,"},{"time":652000,"text":"and was like, \"Hmm. Hmm.\""},{"time":657000,"text":"And he told me, after a long silence,"},{"time":660000,"text":"\"I wonder, Mathieu, if"},{"time":663000,"text":"people won't be more fascinated by your benches"},{"time":665000,"text":"than by my videos.\""},{"time":667000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":670000,"text":"It would be a great honor, a great compliment for me,"},{"time":673000,"text":"if he hadn't decided to take all them off"},{"time":676000,"text":"two hours before the opening."},{"time":678000,"text":"So, huge tragedy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":681000,"text":"I guess you won't be surprised if I tell you"},{"time":683000,"text":"that Pinocchio is one of my great influences."},{"time":686000,"text":"Pinocchio is probably one of my best design products, my favorite one."},{"time":690000,"text":"Because it is a kind of object with a conscience,"},{"time":693000,"text":"able to be modified by its surroundings,"},{"time":695000,"text":"and able to modify it as well."},{"time":698000,"text":"The other great influence is the mine's canary."},{"time":700000,"text":"In coal mines, this canary"},{"time":704000,"text":"was supposed to be close to the miners."},{"time":707000,"text":"And it was singing all day long. And when it stops it means that it just died."},{"time":710000,"text":"So this canary was a living alarm,"},{"time":714000,"text":"and a very efficient one."},{"time":716000,"text":"A very natural technology,"},{"time":718000,"text":"in order to say to the miners,"},{"time":721000,"text":"\"The air is too bad. You have to go. It's an emergency.\""},{"time":726000,"text":"So it's, for me, a great product."}]},{"cues":[{"time":729000,"text":"And I tried to design a kind of canary."},{"time":731000,"text":"Andrea is one."},{"time":733000,"text":"Andrea is a living air filter that absorbs toxic gasses"},{"time":736000,"text":"from air, contaminated indoor air."},{"time":740000,"text":"So it uses some plants to do this job,"},{"time":743000,"text":"selected for their gas-filtering ability."},{"time":748000,"text":"You have to know, or you probably already know,"},{"time":751000,"text":"that indoor air pollution is more toxic than outdoor one."},{"time":754000,"text":"So while I'm talking to you,"},{"time":757000,"text":"the seats you are sitting on are currently emitting some"},{"time":760000,"text":"invisible and odorless toxic gas. Sorry for that. (Laughter)"},{"time":764000,"text":"So you are currently breathing formaldehyde."},{"time":768000,"text":"It's the same for me with the carpet."},{"time":771000,"text":"And this is exactly the same at home."},{"time":775000,"text":"Because all the product we get constantly give away"},{"time":779000,"text":"the volatile component of which they're made of."}]},{"cues":[{"time":782000,"text":"So let's have a look at your home."},{"time":801000,"text":"So your sofa, your plastic chair,"},{"time":803000,"text":"your kid's toys"},{"time":805000,"text":"give their own invisible reality. And this one is very toxic."},{"time":809000,"text":"This is the reason why"},{"time":811000,"text":"I created, with David Edward,"},{"time":813000,"text":"a scientist of Harvard University,"},{"time":815000,"text":"an object able to absorb the toxic elements using those kind of plants."},{"time":821000,"text":"But the idea is to force"},{"time":823000,"text":"the air to go in the effective part of the plants."},{"time":826000,"text":"Because the roots of the plant are not very effective."},{"time":829000,"text":"Bill Wolverton from NASA"},{"time":831000,"text":"analyzed it cleverly in the '70s."},{"time":835000,"text":"So the idea is to create an object"},{"time":837000,"text":"able to force the air, and to be in contact at the right speed"},{"time":841000,"text":"at the right place, in all the effective parts of the plant."},{"time":845000,"text":"So this is the final object."},{"time":847000,"text":"It will be launched next September."},{"time":851000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":854000,"text":"This one is kind of the same approach"},{"time":856000,"text":"because I include, in a product"},{"time":858000,"text":"like Andrea, some plants."},{"time":861000,"text":"And in this one, plants are used for the water filtration ability."},{"time":865000,"text":"And it includes some fishes as well."},{"time":867000,"text":"But here, unlike Andrea,"},{"time":869000,"text":"here are supposed to be eaten."},{"time":871000,"text":"Indeed, this object is a domestic farm,"},{"time":874000,"text":"for fishes and green."},{"time":876000,"text":"So the idea of this object"},{"time":879000,"text":"is to be able to get at home"},{"time":882000,"text":"very local food."},{"time":884000,"text":"The locavores"},{"time":886000,"text":"used to get food"},{"time":888000,"text":"taken in a radius of 100 miles."},{"time":890000,"text":"Local River is able to provide you"},{"time":892000,"text":"food directly in your living room."},{"time":895000,"text":"So the principle of this object"},{"time":898000,"text":"is to create an ecosystem"},{"time":900000,"text":"called aquaponics."},{"time":902000,"text":"And the aquaponics is the dirty water of the fish,"},{"time":906000,"text":"by a water pump, feeds the plants above."},{"time":909000,"text":"And the plants will filter, by the roots,"},{"time":912000,"text":"the dirty water of the fish."},{"time":914000,"text":"After, it goes back into the fish tank."}]},{"cues":[{"time":918000,"text":"After that you have two options."},{"time":920000,"text":"Or you sit down in front of it like you would do in front your TV set."},{"time":923000,"text":"Amazing channel."},{"time":926000,"text":"Or you start fishing."},{"time":928000,"text":"And you make some sushis with a fish"},{"time":931000,"text":"and the aromatic plants above."},{"time":933000,"text":"Because you can grow some potatoes."},{"time":935000,"text":"No, not potatoes, but tomatoes,"},{"time":937000,"text":"aromatic plants and so on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":939000,"text":"So now we can breathe safely."},{"time":942000,"text":"Now we can eat local food."},{"time":945000,"text":"Now we can be treated by smart medicine."},{"time":948000,"text":"Now we can be well-balanced in our biorhythm"},{"time":951000,"text":"with daylight."},{"time":953000,"text":"But it was important to create a perfect place,"},{"time":956000,"text":"so I tried to,"},{"time":958000,"text":"in order to work and create."},{"time":961000,"text":"So I designed, for an American scientist based in Paris,"},{"time":965000,"text":"a very stimulative, brain-stimulative office."},{"time":968000,"text":"I wanted to create a perfect place"},{"time":971000,"text":"where you can work and play,"},{"time":973000,"text":"and where your body and your brain can work together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":976000,"text":"So, in this office,"},{"time":978000,"text":"you do not work anymore at your desk, like a politician."},{"time":982000,"text":"Your seat, your sleep and your play"},{"time":986000,"text":"on a big geodesic island made of leather."},{"time":990000,"text":"See, like this one?"},{"time":992000,"text":"In this office you do not work and write and draw on a sheet of paper,"},{"time":997000,"text":"but you draw directly on a kind of huge whiteboard cave,"},{"time":1002000,"text":"like a prehistoric scientist."},{"time":1004000,"text":"So you, like that, can make some sport during your work."},{"time":1008000,"text":"In this office"},{"time":1012000,"text":"you do not need to go out"},{"time":1014000,"text":"in order to be in contact with nature."},{"time":1017000,"text":"You include, directly, the nature in the floor of the office."},{"time":1022000,"text":"You can see it there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1025000,"text":"This is an inspiration image"},{"time":1027000,"text":"to lead this project of the office."},{"time":1029000,"text":"It really helped me to design it."},{"time":1031000,"text":"I never show it to my client. He would be so afraid."},{"time":1034000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1035000,"text":"Just for my workshop."},{"time":1038000,"text":"I guess it may be the revenge of the guinea pig I was."},{"time":1042000,"text":"But it's maybe the conviction"},{"time":1046000,"text":"as monkey and homunculus we are."},{"time":1050000,"text":"All of us need to be considered according to our real nature."},{"time":1056000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":1058000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}